Revision history for Perl extension Deep::Encode.

0.01  Thu Sep  2 16:17:05 2010
	- original version; created by h2xs 1.23 with options
		-AfO -n Deep::Encode
0.02  Thu Sep  3 10:17:15 2010
	- Added subs:
	deep_utf8_decode
	deep_utf8_encode
	and
	deep_str_process (experimental)


0.03  Thu Sep  8 18:15 2010
	- Added subs:
	deep_fromto
	deep_encode
	deep_decode
	- Apply some optimizations and lot of profiling

0.04  Mon Sep 20 13:00:13 MSK 2010
    - Added fastcall for deep_* so all functions performs faster
    - Added some tests
    - Added documentation for deep_encode deep_decode


0.05  Mon Sep 20 14:54:13 MSK 2010
    - Typos in code

0.06  Mon Sep 27 23:59:59 MSK 2010
    - Fix documentation

0.07  Tue Oct 5 17:15 MSK 2010
    - Added deep_utf8_off

0.08  Wen Oct 6 20:50 MSK 2010
    - Added deep_utf8_upgrade
    - Added deep_utf8_downgrade
    - Little more tests

0.09  Wen Oct 7 10:31 MSK 2010
    - deep_utf8_check
    - test deep_utf8_check

0.10  Wen Oct 7 11:47 MSK 2010
    - test for some  magic in deep_utf8_check

